{"tid":1521763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"現場消息快過連登好多，要叫散水自己落場叫","createTime":"2019-08-31T10:43:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T14:07:42.000Z","uid":33307,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a37b995bb1af482df3bbfc87290e64f0d5ba4b51","tid":1521763,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:43:36.000Z","msg":"係度叫春冇用"},{"pid":"e013766c564926782e6e5c1de8e8c5a7e2809011","tid":1521763,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:44:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/etSapPa.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FetSapPa.gif&h=0cba6709&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=l3PzQMWIA05fFBLp0mk4WoaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=d934d991\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=l3PzQMWIA05fFBLp0mk4WoaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=b0348c3d\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=l3PzQMWIA05fFBLp0mk4WoaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=473461f8\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"886717f88c09e92d0d4a4db4e3a29f51580d9f6f","tid":1521763,"uid":220775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:44:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"242eb1db365f46db8436da0ef84d948b24785c65","tid":1521763,"uid":139282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:44:40.000Z","msg":"［化學］如何清洗顏色水劑（含acrylics/PMMA）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1406604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1406604</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n1. hot sodium carbonate solution<br />\n<br />\n-蘇打水，溫度50度或更高，建議自己開，落多小小都唔怕<br />\n（同小蘇打sodium bicarbonate有啲分別，唔知bicarbonate效果係點）<br />\n<br />\n2.消毒火酒（酒精）/含消毒火酒成份濕紙巾<br />\n<br />\n3.化妝水/卸妝水/洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n可以洗到有acrylics/PMMA嘅顏料<br />\n<br />\n紅字係考慮完availability, effectiveness, usefulness, side-effects嘅建議<br />\n<br />\n另外衫褲鞋襪可以先噴防水噴霧<br />\n中招就唔好留直接dum咗佢<br />\n<br />\n消毒火酒：<br />\n易買 平 可用作消毒 但係多用傷皮膚<br />\n化/卸妝水：<br />\n女仔會有 比較唔傷皮膚 但貴 同埋唔同牌子效果可能會有差異<br />\n<br />\n其他建議：<br />\n#67 威猛先生玻璃劑<br />\n#91 含酒精成分濕紙巾<br />\n#117 大塊顏料可以待乾再成塊搣<br />\n<br />\n#127<br />\n可以搽定凡士林/hand cream<br />\n保持皮膚濕潤方便移除顏料<br />\n<br />\n#145<br />\n唔敢去五金可以去模型舖買Mr Color paint remover/Mr Color tool cleaner，冇就買住水性油天拿水頂住先<br />\n<br />\n#148<br />\n補充使用順序：<br />\n先用水性油天拿水或者75%酒精捽<br />\n好頑固捽唔到嗰啲先用paint remover/tool cleaner<br />\n因為用完呢兩隻，啲顏料會變硝基，用唔返酒精<br />\n最後都唔得先好用洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n#164<br />\n凡士林coating，logon $50 gel removal"},{"pid":"5c7b4539428c2060848b29669d6e11c3720b3df8","tid":1521763,"uid":237809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:44:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a25970b6df081ddd7cb50919611b1de91b0aca2e","tid":1521763,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T10:45:01.000Z","msg":"我係一個出左銅鑼灣既耶撚<br />\n<br />\n前線唔會有時間去上連登，而且上網收得極差，佢地唔會睇到大家對行動既意見，而家唔係不停開新post去屌人或者去比意見既時候，而係：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果你係一個睇緊直播既冷氣軍師</span><br />\n請你地幫手推一啲實際既行動 / 文宣post，並準備好落街接放學既準備<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果你係一個已經係街既非前線</span><br />\n請幫手推同更新一啲現場直擊post，並做好哨兵既角色，隨時支援前線<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果你係一個仲睇到呢個post既前線</span><br />\n幫我同前線講聲加油！一定要注意安全，人人都係哨兵，齊上齊落，唔好比任何一個手足落單<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山，各自努力，互相支援</span>"},{"pid":"8426b00e42e7a602fd87797e9451068cb9430329","tid":1521763,"uid":114801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T14:06:20.000Z","msg":"推你上去比人block, <br />\n<br />\n屌你老母，開十鳩幾個post鼓吹死守"},{"pid":"a8d89ff446cb05548a945baaf285fc35e978f854","tid":1521763,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T14:07:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不割蓆、不譴責、不篤灰</strong></span></span>"}]}